headline: Better Artificial Intelligence Stock: Palantir vs. Nvidia
summary: Two of the hottest artificial intelligence (AI) stocks in 2024 were, no doubt, Palantir (NASDAQ: PLTR) and Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA).  Let's look at which stock is the better investment option for investors right now.  Palantir and Nvidia have two very different businesses, but both have been big AI winners.
